                        "description":  "On a failed Intelligence save, the target treats every visible creature as an enemy for up to 1 minute with concentration, chooses targets randomly from visible creatures in range, and must make available opportunity attacks. A target immune to Frightened automatically succeeds, and damage lets the target repeat the Intelligence save to end the effect.",
